Dialogue: 100,0:00:32.86,0:00:35.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}\N{\rENG}Whoa! 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:51.78,0:00:53.21,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}\N{\rENG}Aah! Aah! 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:54.08,0:00:55.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你们俩能融合?!\N{\rENG}You two can fuse?! 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:55.92,0:00:57.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃...是的?\N{\rENG}Uh...Yes? 
