Dialogue: 100,0:01:05.66,0:01:08.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}求求你后不要告诉我家长 宇宙先生!\N{\rENG}Please don't tell my parents, Mr. Universe. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:08.16,0:01:10.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他们不知道我一直在和史蒂文与魔法打交道\N{\rENG}They don't know I've been doing magic stuff with Steven. 
