Dialogue: 100,0:01:25.95,0:01:27.51,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}来吧\N{\rENG}Come on. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:24.08,0:01:25.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}故事!\N{\rENG}Story! 
