Dialogue: 100,0:04:07.94,0:04:10.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不敢相信我录到了那个!\N{\rENG}I can't believe I got that on video! 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:10.45,0:04:12.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}地球上有这玩意?\N{\rENG}What on earth was that?! 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:12.28,0:04:14.95,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那是彩虹石英啊\N{\rENG}That was rainbow Quartz. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:14.95,0:04:16.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}珍珠觉得融合体\N{\rENG}Pearl thought a fusion
Dialogue: 100,0:04:16.28,0:04:18.95,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}能给你的视频加点料\N{\rENG}might give your video a little something extra. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:18.95,0:04:21.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这很酷 对吧?\N{\rENG}Pretty cool, right? 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:21.49,0:04:25.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我得走了 但晚些时候忙吗吗?\N{\rENG}I have to go, but are you doing anything later? 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:25.26,0:04:27.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你知道我没事\N{\rENG}You know I'm not. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:28.13,0:04:30.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你真可爱 宇宙先生\N{\rENG}You're adorable, Mr. Universe. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:30.17,0:04:31.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一会见\N{\rENG}See you later. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:31.70,0:04:34.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}拜拜\N{\rENG}Bye. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:34.67,0:04:39.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 我打鼓了 赶紧付钱\N{\rENG}Hey, I hit the drums, so pay up. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:39.01,0:04:40.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这个给你\N{\rENG}Here you go. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:44.48,0:04:48.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你只是个过客. 你知道吧?--不\N{\rENG}You're just a phase. You know that, right? No. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:50.65,0:04:52.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我实际上不知道 珍珠\N{\rENG}I actually don't know that, Pearl. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:52.56,0:04:54.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哈 当然你不知道\N{\rENG}Well, of course you don't. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:54.49,0:04:56.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你一点也不了解玫瑰\N{\rENG}You don't know anything about Rose. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:56.49,0:04:58.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我知道那超喜欢我\N{\rENG}I know she's super into me. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:58.49,0:05:01.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}听着 宇宙先生\N{\rENG}Listen Mr. Universe. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:01.20,0:05:03.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}玫瑰也许觉得你很有魅力\N{\rENG}Rose may find you charming, 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:03.53,0:05:05.83,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但这只是因为你是个人类\N{\rENG}but that's only because you're human. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:05.83,0:05:08.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你最多只是新奇而已\N{\rENG}You're a novelty at best. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:08.07,0:05:10.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你怎么这么确定?\N{\rENG}What makes you so sure? 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:10.00,0:05:12.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 很明显.\N{\rENG}Oh it's very simple. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:12.38,0:05:14.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}人类不能融合\N{\rENG}Humans can't fuse. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:14.34,0:05:18.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}融合是宝石人之间最终极的联系\N{\rENG}Fusion is the ultimate connection between gems. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:18.15,0:05:20.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而你不是宝石人\N{\rENG}And you are not a gem. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:22.25,0:05:26.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那么 就没有任何人类尝试过与宝石人融合吗?\N{\rENG}Well, has any human ever tried fusing with a gem? 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:26.02,0:05:30.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 没有 我-我不觉得会有\N{\rENG}Uh, no, I-I don't think so. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:30.02,0:05:32.83,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好 那么 我会!\N{\rENG}Well, then, i will try! 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:36.33,0:05:37.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 天哪 我在干嘛?\N{\rENG}Aw, geez, what am I doing? 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:37.50,0:05:39.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这些东西很贵的\N{\rENG}These things are expensive. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:43.20,0:05:46.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}天哪! 她是怎么把腿抬成那样的?\N{\rENG}Oh, geez! How did she get her legs to do that? 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:48.21,0:05:49.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿. 你挂了吗?\N{\rENG}Hey. Are you dead? 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:49.34,0:05:52.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}蛤? 哦 不 不. 我还活着\N{\rENG}What? Oh, no no. I'm alive. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:52.05,0:05:53.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}喔 酷!\N{\rENG}Whoa, cool! 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:53.55,0:05:55.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这是刚才的我们\N{\rENG}Aah. It's us from before. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:55.92,0:05:57.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}对 我正试着\N{\rENG}Yeah, I was just trying to
Dialogue: 100,0:05:57.59,0:05:59.59,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}用脑子搞清楚融合舞呢\N{\rENG}get my head around this fusion dance. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:59.59,0:06:02.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}融合舞和脑子没关系!\N{\rENG}A fusion dance ain't about your head! 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:03.36,0:06:05.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等等 你们是宝石人\N{\rENG}Wait, you guys are gems. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:05.53,0:06:06.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你们一定要帮帮我啊\N{\rENG}You've got to help me out here. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:06.86,0:06:09.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我想要和罗丝融合\N{\rENG}I need to be able to fuse with Rose. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:09.40,0:06:11.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}首先 你需要有一个宝石作为存在的基础\N{\rENG}First, you need the gem at the core of your being. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:11.90,0:06:14.43,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}然后 你需要一个能变成光的身体\N{\rENG}Then you need the body that could turn into light. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:14.44,0:06:17.27,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}之后 你需要一个你能信任的变成光的同伴\N{\rENG}Then you need the partner who you trust with that light. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:17.27,0:06:18.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这是比喻?\N{\rENG}Metaphorically? 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:18.94,0:06:20.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}并不\N{\rENG}Literally. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:20.24,0:06:23.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘘. 别啊 我还想看他试试\N{\rENG}Shh. Come on. I still want to see him try. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:23.41,0:06:26.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 珍珠是对的. 我完全做不到\N{\rENG}Ugh, so it's true. I really can't do it. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:26.58,0:06:28.61,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我简直在跟自己开玩笑\N{\rENG}I'm kidding myself with this. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:28.62,0:06:30.65,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我永远也不可能变成宝石人\N{\rENG}I'm never gonna be a gem. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:31.29,0:06:34.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}紫晶 给我们点私密空间\N{\rENG}Amethyst, give us some privacy! 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:34.29,0:06:36.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好!\N{\rENG}Yeah! 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:36.29,0:06:38.39,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我告诉你点秘密 宇宙先生\N{\rENG}Let me tell you something, Mr. Universe. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:38.39,0:06:39.79,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我觉得你能做到\N{\rENG}I think you can do it. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:39.79,0:06:42.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但像珍珠那样跳舞并没有用\N{\rENG}But it won't work if you dance like Pearl. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:42.06,0:06:44.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你要跳出自己的风格\N{\rENG}You have to dance like you. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:44.10,0:06:46.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你要有自己的融合的方式\N{\rENG}You have to fuse your way. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:46.07,0:06:48.27,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}做到开放 坦诚\N{\rENG}Get open. Get honest. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:48.27,0:06:52.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}坚持自我. 这就是融合\N{\rENG}Invent yourselves together. That's fusion. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:52.01,0:06:54.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}眼...猜我了解了.\N{\rENG}Eye...Think I get it. 
Dialogue: 600,0:07:08.00,0:07:11.00,Hint,,0,0,0,,此处舞蹈与布景致敬少女革命: 绝对命运默示录
Dialogue: 100,0:07:38.29,0:07:40.99,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们-我们没融合\N{\rENG}We--we didn't fuse. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:41.60,0:07:42.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊?!\N{\rENG}What?! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:44.34,0:07:46.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你肯定不能融合\N{\rENG}You can't fuse. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:46.90,0:07:48.83,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你是人类\N{\rENG}You're a human. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:48.83,0:07:51.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我知道! 这就是问题!\N{\rENG}I know! That's the problem! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:51.00,0:07:52.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我只是个人类\N{\rENG}I'm just a human. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:52.20,0:07:55.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这不是问题. 我爱人类\N{\rENG}That's not a problem. I love humans. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:55.97,0:07:57.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你们都那么有趣\N{\rENG}You're all so funny. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:57.84,0:07:58.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊\N{\rENG}Ugh. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:58.80,0:08:01.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}听着 过去几个月非常美好--哦 是的\N{\rENG}Look, these last few months have been great. Oh, yes. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:01.84,0:08:04.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但我开始对将来有些担心\N{\rENG}But I'm getting a little worried about the future. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:04.05,0:08:05.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 那问问石榴\N{\rENG}Oh, just ask Garnet. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:05.68,0:08:09.25,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我开始怀疑你是否...在乎我?\N{\rENG}I'm starting to wonder if you...Respect me? 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:11.59,0:08:15.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 你真幽默 宇宙先生\N{\rENG}Oh, you're hilarious, Mr. Universe. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:15.19,0:08:17.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}罗丝 求求你\N{\rENG}Rose, please. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:17.19,0:08:19.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你能不能\N{\rENG}Can you just...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:19.06,0:08:23.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}和我说人话 哪怕是一秒?\N{\rENG}Talk to me for one second like a real person?! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:27.03,0:08:30.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我...不是人类\N{\rENG}I'm nota real person. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:31.94,0:08:34.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我以为-我们难道还没-\N{\rENG}I thought--haven't we--
Dialogue: 100,0:08:34.74,0:08:37.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}难道不该这样吗?\N{\rENG}is this not how it works? 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:37.98,0:08:38.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢\N{\rENG}Oh. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:39.40,0:08:40.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 天哪\N{\rENG}Oh, boy. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:40.75,0:08:43.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这太诡异了. 你真是个外星人\N{\rENG}This is so weird. You really are an alien. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:45.89,0:08:47.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你为什么笑了?\N{\rENG}Why are you laughing? 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:49.06,0:08:50.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你怎么又哭了?\N{\rENG}Why are you crying? 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:50.56,0:08:53.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们该怎么办?\N{\rENG}How are we gonna make this work? 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:53.70,0:08:54.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}融合?\N{\rENG}Fusion? 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:54.73,0:08:56.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不 是我们的关系\N{\rENG}No, us. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:56.23,0:08:59.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们真的 非常不同\N{\rENG}We're really, really different. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:59.30,0:09:01.43,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们现在该怎么办?\N{\rENG}What do we do now? 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:01.44,0:09:06.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们先...聊聊吧\N{\rENG}Let's just...Talk. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:06.24,0:09:07.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我根本不了解你\N{\rENG}I barely know you. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:07.91,0:09:08.87,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这是个好事\N{\rENG}That's a good thing. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:08.88,0:09:10.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们的关系进展的真有点快了\N{\rENG}We really rushed into this. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:10.75,0:09:13.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}地球上的一切对我来讲都太快了\N{\rENG}Everything on earth seems fast to me. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:13.58,0:09:16.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你想念你的母星吗?\N{\rENG}Do you miss your home planet? 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:16.75,0:09:18.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不 从不\N{\rENG}No. Never. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:18.05,0:09:21.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你最后是怎么和 呃 走到一起的?\N{\rENG}How did you end up with, uh, Harpo, Groucho, and chico? 
Dialogue: 600,0:09:18.05,0:09:21.32,Hint,,0,0,0,,Harpo Groucho和Chico是Marx Brothers( 马克斯兄弟) 的成员.\NMarx Brothers是美国喜剧界早期著名团体 与卓别林 劳埃德齐名 擅长无政府主义风格.\NHarpo对应石榴( 沉默寡言) Groucho对应紫晶( 直率) Chico( 经常有夸张行为) 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:21.32,0:09:23.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊? 哦 她们\N{\rENG}Huh? Oh, them. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:23.78,0:09:25.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她们三个的故事可长了\N{\rENG}Those are three long stories. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:25.52,0:09:27.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他们在干吗?--嘘!\N{\rENG}What are they doing? Shh! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:27.26,0:09:29.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你喜欢过其他人类吗?\N{\rENG}Have you loved other humans? 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:30.62,0:09:31.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你呢?\N{\rENG}Have you? 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:31.93,0:09:33.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}有--有\N{\rENG}Yes. Yes. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:33.64,0:09:37.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那你 爱过 人类吗?\N{\rENG}Have you ever been in love with a human? 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:37.14,0:09:38.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我怎么知道?\N{\rENG}How would I know? 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:38.44,0:09:40.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这是一种折磨\N{\rENG}It's torture. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:42.94,0:09:44.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}格雷格\N{\rENG}Greg. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:44.01,0:09:45.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}罗丝\N{\rENG}Rose. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:45.58,0:09:47.45,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这是折磨吗?\N{\rENG}Is this torture? 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:47.45,0:09:48.81,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}最可怕的那种\N{\rENG}The worst. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:48.82,0:09:50.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我实在对不起\N{\rENG}I'm so sorry. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:50.92,0:09:53.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊? 不 不用\N{\rENG}Huh? No. Don't be. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:53.02,0:09:55.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}为什么?!\N{\rENG}What?! Why not?! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:55.02,0:09:57.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢 我太困惑了!\N{\rENG}Me, too. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:57.26,0:09:58.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我也是\N{\rENG}Me, too. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:58.59,0:10:00.59,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那么 呃 这不错\N{\rENG}Well, uh, this is good. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:00.60,0:10:02.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们总算有一个共同点了\N{\rENG}We've got one thing in common. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:02.96,0:10:04.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}\N{\rENG}Ha! Ohh! 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:06.27,0:10:07.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他们还在跳舞?\N{\rENG}Why are they still dancing? 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:07.60,0:10:08.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那-那-那根本行不通啊\N{\rENG}I-I-it didn't work. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:08.94,0:10:11.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不 他们成了.--啊?!\N{\rENG}Yes, it did. What?! 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:11.37,0:10:12.87,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}已经成功了\N{\rENG}It worked. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:12.87,0:10:15.61,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我觉得这是我最喜欢的人类\N{\rENG}I think this one's my favorite. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:15.61,0:10:19.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我觉得他也是她最喜欢的人了\N{\rENG}I think he's her favorite, too. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:21.78,0:10:23.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}喔\N{\rENG}Whoa. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:23.12,0:10:25.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那么 你们一直都不能融合?\N{\rENG}So, you guys were never able to fuse? 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:25.49,0:10:26.89,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 不能\N{\rENG}Uh, no. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:26.89,0:10:29.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但那不如与对方沟通重要\N{\rENG}But that wasn't as important as talking to each other. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:29.60,0:10:31.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}听着 人类和宝石人--\N{\rENG}Look, humans and gems--
Dialogue: 100,0:10:31.69,0:10:33.79,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这仍是一个未知的领域\N{\rENG}it's still some pretty new territory. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:33.80,0:10:35.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你们需要共同探索\N{\rENG}You're gonna have to work it out together. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:35.80,0:10:37.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而且 康妮 如果你需要\N{\rENG}And, Connie, if you ever need to talk
Dialogue: 100,0:10:37.80,0:10:39.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}向另一个人类谈论此事\N{\rENG}to another human being about this, 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:39.50,0:10:41.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你永远可以找我\N{\rENG}you can always talk to me. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:41.70,0:10:42.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嗯\N{\rENG}Mm. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:42.50,0:10:44.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}人类一族?\N{\rENG}Human beings? 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:44.04,0:10:45.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}人类一族\N{\rENG}Human beings. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:45.92,0:10:47.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}人类一族\N{\rENG}Human beings. 
